ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Customs Tariff (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations amending CERTAIN MADE UNDER THE CUSTOMS TARIFF (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to support the seamless transition from the North American Free Trade Agreement to Canada-United States-Mexico Agreement (CUSMA) and to ensure stakeholders will have current and clear regulations in place at the time of implementation of CUSMA.
